	Add -DX_LOCALE to CPPFLAGS.

	* Makefile.am
	* doc/Makefile.am
	* test/Makefile.am
	* test/bootstrap:
	Fixed *clean make targets.

	* lib/perl.cygclass (perl_compile):
	Don't pass --prefix /usr to Build.PL after all.

	* README: Various updates.

	* lib/gst-plugins.cygclass (gst_plugins_autoreconf):
	GStreamer tarballs include autogen.sh, so use it instead.
	Add files generated by autogen.sh to DIFF_EXCLUDES.

	* lib/ruby.cygclass (ruby_compile, ruby_install):
	Accept arguments and pass them to appropriate commands.

	* lib/gst-plugins.cygclass (gst_plugins_autoreconf):
	Use gnome2_autoreconf to avoid breaking po/Makefile.in.in.

	* bin/cygport.in (verbose, cygconf)
	* lib/cvs.cygclass (cvs_unpack)
	* lib/gnome2.cygclass (gnome2_autoreconf)
	* lib/svn.cygclass (svn_unpack):
	New function to print a command before execution, as make does.
	Use throughout.

	* bin/cygport.in (pkg_pkgcheck):
	Only warn where files are missing, as there are cases where that's 
	acceptable, but error if files are duplicated.

	* bin/cygport.in (pkg_diff):
	Ignore intltool.m4, except for within intltool.
	Ignore omf.make and xmldocs.make, except for within gnome-common.

	* lib/xorg.cygclass:
	Don't force WANT_AUTOMAKE.

	* lib/gnome2.cygclass (gnome2_autoreconf):
	Only pass --force to aclocal-1.8/1.9; earlier versions don't accept it.

	* configure.ac:
	Post-release version bump.

